Here's What You Will Learn:

Big Picture & Big Markets: How to get it? How to get it? How to get there? What are the critical success factors for long-term growth? 
Market-Driven Product Development: in portable, stationary and automotive arenas 
Premium Power Markets: Which ones make sense to fuel cell manufacturers? 
Future Applications: Closer than you think? 
Solving the Hydrogen Equation: Who is going to finance it? How to find liquid fuels? What role will fuel cells & hydrogen play? 


